name: Victorian Rains
description:
I love this Parasol it is so feminine. This is an 80cm black rain parasol with a double thickness frill , to create fullness in the look. 
The frill is 14cm wide and trimmed in a delicate black lace and luscious velvet ribbon.
Victorian Rains has been the biggest seller throughout winter. 
What a special parasol for a winter look.

More pictures available on request
All parasols are shower proof and handmade.
All designs are handmade from the artist.
Australian made.

name: Victorian Black Lace
description:
I had a strong influence from the Victorian Era with this look.

A stunning patterned lace (not see through) cover that spans 100cm in width with black lace trimming and a delicate black bow on each tip.
The length is 80 cm ending in a gorgeous black velvet ribbon and twine handle.

This parasol also comes in  cream  with long cream fringing.
Pictures available on request.

All parasols are shower proof and can be made to an 80cm width.
All designs are handmade from the artist.
Australian made.

name: Sultry Summer Shade
description:
Have an alluring summer with this gorgeous Parasol. Peer through sheer black lace 12cm wide that just falls the right way , whilst shading your precious skin from the biting sun. 

At 80cm wide and 90cm long this delicate little Parasol has a darling handle made from velvet ribbon and twine.

name: Summer cooler... Pink Pom-Pom Parasol.
description:
This Parasol has a  fresh white cotton skin with a coloured floral bouquet design, trimmed in pink pom-poms, pink velvet ribbon , velvet and twine handle.
Shady lady parasols will protect your beautiful skin from the ravages of the sun , whilst complimenting that special look . 

This parasol comes in 3 different fabrics with matching pom-poms pictures can be emailed.


All parasols are shower proof .
